[{\cite{CFW},\cite[Appendix A]{FKSV}}] \label{theorem:appendix}
Let $G \curvearrowright X$ be a continuous action of a countable group on a Polish space. The following are equivalent:
\begin{enumerate}
\item $G \curvearrowright X$ is topologically amenable,
\item $E_G^X$ is measure-hyperfinite and every stabilizer is amenable.
\end{enumerate}

